SummaryEnglish: First-year middle school girls Mirai Momoyama and Emo Moegi are two aspiring idols who decide to use the "Pri☆Chan System," a system used by famous people and companies to broadcast content. Like many girls starting their own channels and uploading content, the pair decide to become their own producers, starting their own channel in an attempt to become Pri☆Chan idols.

1.TitleEnglish: A Sparkling PriChan? I Tried It!
1.SummaryEnglish: After a failed attempt at getting an autograph from the most popular PriChan idol, Anna Akagi, Mirai finds herself thrust into the world of idols after Emo accepts a challenge from Anna.

2.TitleEnglish: PriChanning From a Flower Shop? We Tried It!
2.SummaryEnglish: Mirai and Emo fear they are not cut out for the hectic world of Idols after they try to participate in a variety program by assisting a flower shop; on top of dealing with interviews and recording. But to their surprise, a friend shows up to help them...

3.TitleEnglish: Write an Idol Song? I Tried It!
3.SummaryEnglish: To improve their Home Page the girls decide to come up with an official name for themselves. As this is going on Mirai finds herself coerced into entering the "Free Style Poemy" competition- where the winner will receive their own, special song for use.

4.SummaryEnglish: In hopes of bringing in more sales to their families sweet shop, Mirai and her friends decide to make a video about it. But after it blows into a full-on competition Anna and Sara decide to compete with them to see who can make the best sweet and wow the crowd!

5.TitleEnglish: Heating Things up With Guts? We Tried It!
5.SummaryEnglish: The girls have been doing increasingly well; but after Anna accuses of them of being unable to ignite the warmth of passion in people, Meganee enters them in upcoming Fluffy Castle event. But with Emo's twisted ankle and Anna hijacking the event- will Mirai be able to conquer the Athletic challenge?!

6.SummaryEnglish: For Emo, she expresses her support and love for others by cheering for them whenever she can. But after her younger brother tells her off for embarrassing him, she struggles to understand his feelings while losing her passion to do anything.

7.TitleEnglish: Film a Cat Video? We Tried It!
7.SummaryEnglish: After finding a stray cat the girls decide to make a Cat video in hopes of finding its owner- but Emo is horrified of cats! Can she overcome this fear and help make the video a success?

8.TitleEnglish: Dress Up With Hair and Makeup? We Tried It!
8.SummaryEnglish: A popular fashion Magazine is looking for Idol models- but first those trying out must submit a makeup video and gain the most Likes to win the role. Mirai and Emo, who know nothing about makeup turn to a friend for support but she struggles approaching PriChan...

9.SummaryEnglish: Anna is personally issued a challenge by Emo to put on an amazing performance worthy of their attention after she takes her constant criticism too far. But as she hasn't performed in PriChan for a long time, is Anna capable of meeting a challenge that reminds her of a painful past event?
